      "body_text": "Code Analysis:\\n\\nIt looks like `net.minecraft.client.gui.components.AbstractWidget#isMouseOver` now checks if the element `isNarratable`???\\n\\nThis makes absolutely no sense, as the mouse can also be hovered over elements that are not narratable.\\n\\n",
      "body_length": 251,
      "rendered_body": "<p>Code Analysis:</p>\n\n<p>It looks like <tt>net.minecraft.client.gui.components.AbstractWidget#isMouseOver</tt> now checks if the element <tt>isNarratable</tt>???</p>\n\n<p>This makes absolutely no sense, as the mouse can also be hovered over elements that are not narratable.</p>",
      "body": {
        "type": "doc",
        "version": 1,
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Code Analysis:"
